id=odin3_hdr_brightness_fix
name=Odin 3 HDR Fix
version=v1.1.0
versionCode=2
author=kingaetheral, WhiteEagle-12, Zurce
description=Systemless Odin 3 HDR display fix: overlays the correct panel display config, applies HDR display properties, and optionally keeps the SurfaceFlinger composition workaround active with a watchdog. Best used with the companion DTBO peak-brightness patcher.
